      "raw_text": "The British Columbia Copper Co.\nresumed operations at the mine\nand smelter near Phoenix in the\nboundary district today with work\nfor 700 men. Indications are that\nthe rlning industry OF this district\nwill he running again at full swing\nas soon as the required number of\nminers can be put to work.\n\n\nThe Last Chance mine at Ward\nner, Idaho, is to resume work next\nMonday. 1t is understood that 300\nmen will be put to work there."
